Alias      MyD*-       D*-
Alias      MyD*+       D*+
ChargeConj MyD*+       MyD*-
#
Alias      MyD0        D0
Alias Myanti-D0   anti-D0
ChargeConj        MyD0       Myanti-D0
#
Alias      MyK_S0      K_S0
