Decay B0sig
0.70   MyD*- Mya_1+                      SVV_HELAMP 0.200 0.0 0.866 0.0 0.458 0.0; 
0.13   MyD*-  Myf_2  pi+                PHSP;
0.12   MyD*-  rho0  pi+                  PHSP;
0.05   MyD*-  pi+ pi- pi+                PHSP;
Enddecay
CDecay anti-B0sig
#
Decay Myanti-D0
